descriptionHtml:
What does it do:
-Set your stats into SUPER high level
-Unlock all map markers
-Give you all dragon shouts (Dawnguard And Dragonborn Shouts too :D)
-Set all skills to 100
-Unlock all perks
-Unlock all spells
-Gives you all amulets
-Gives you Some rare armor
If you don't have any dlcs,delete the shouts and the spells
In case,if the shouts or spells doesn't work,then change the load order (i use the unofficial patches)
To change the load order,open the fap.txt and search for the unworking spells/shouts (the xx means the load order,some of them i already changed because i have the unofficial patches)
Link:
http://elderscrolls.wikia.com/wiki/Console_Commands_%28Skyrim%29/Spells

(This doesn't contain tons of items like flugudrave,only some rare items)
